1. Make sure that you have 'cmake' package.

$ export PATH=/afs/cern.ch/compass/detector/straw/bin:$PATH

2. Go to some directotry where you will build the files:

$ cd STRAW-soft.git/coral/macros

3. Create a directory where you will 'build' the project:

$ mkdir cbuild

4. Configure it:

$ cd cbuild
$ cmake ..
$ make

5. Install it:

  -- Choose  a location:
  $ ccmake ..
  
  And change CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX
  
  -- Install it:
  $ make install
